Text: The FIRST thing you need to know when it comes to sex is CONSENT. Before you do anything, you need to make sure both you and YOUR PARTNER agree to whatever’s about to go down. That’s consent. It doesn’t matter if it’s head, sex, kissing, or even grinding, you need to get consent. And it doesn’t have to be complicated.
